The paper discusses the application of wavelet packet transform for spectrum sensing, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), signal processing (cs.SP), and networking (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the performance metrics such as variance of the estimated power spectral density (PSD), which is a topic related to statistical inference (cs.ST) and machine learning (cs.LG).
